50|$|In CSS, a font-family (or face in HTML) {{consists}} {{of a set of}} related fonts, grouped as <b>font</b> <b>families.</b> For example, the Times <b>family</b> includes different <b>font</b> sizes, styles (like roman and italic), and weight (like regular and bold).|$|R
